Gameram is a social network for everyone who plays games! 
Mobile, PC, consoles or board games – everyone is welcome.

SHARE emotions from gaming with your friends - post screenshots and videos;
FIND new friends and teammates - post your gaming IDs to play together, discuss games you like;
CELEBRATE your achievements (or failures:) ), laugh together at funny moments and support each other with tips and advice.

Your feedback is vital to making the Gameram even better, so we’d love to hear your thoughts: support@gameram.com
